<p align="center">In the near future a proctor will be required to submit a Proctor Certification Form.</p>
<p><strong>1) The student notifies BYU-Idaho that they have located a proctor</strong></p>
<p>After you have found a proctor to administer your exam click on the button below and fill out the Proctor Request Form for each test that you take. Please respond to every item requested on the form. <strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Incomplete or inaccurate information</span></strong> will cause delays in providing your proctor with permission to proceed with the exam.</p>
<table border="1" cellpadding="0" width="130">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>
<p align="center"><strong><a href="http://www.byui.edu/OnLinetesting/Pages/FormSTDRequest.html" title="Proctor Request Information Form" target="_parent">Proctor Request Form</a></strong></p>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p align="center"><strong>Please allow 2 full business days for us to provide instructions to the proctor! </strong></p>
<p><strong>2) BYU-Idaho contacts the proctor</strong></p>
<p> </p>
<p>After you have filled out and submitted the proctor form, BYU-Idaho will respond to the Proctor with the instructions and password for the test and the student will be notified that they may now set a time and date for the test to be taken.  Please remember to give us two full working days to contact the Proctor.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Please remember that we are not in the office on weekends and holidays. </strong></p>
<p><strong>Exam Procedure</strong></p>
<p>After your proctor has been approved, he or she will be sent instructions for the exam and you will meet at the specified time and location. When the exam is finished, the proctor will send an e-mail message to <a href="mailto:OnlineLearning@byui.edu" target="_parent">The BYU-Idaho Testing Center</a>. This message is the official indication that the exam has been taken. In this final e-mail message, the proctor will confirm that the proctoring conditions listed above were met.</p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded=""><xPower Type="List" List="xpowercomponent_Optional" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="QuickLinks Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent"/></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Navigation" StartPage="x5" MaxDepth="" MaxNodes="" GenerationOrder="down" Navigation="Ancestors" Query="" Name="AncestorNavigation" label="Ancestor Navig